Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.00,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}翻译：傻瓜三世 ZERO 逆火 校对：傻瓜三世\N\N后期：Misaki喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁叫你穿那么厚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以不用练了吧 比赛都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可不行 回程还有一场跳长绳大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看到获胜队伍是吃什么肉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么可以吊车尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少不能再吃鱼肉香肠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为那可不算肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑好会跳绳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不是奇怪 就是你给人不会跳的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑是人不可貌相的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比方说不可貌相的蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可貌相的急性子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可貌相的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们什么意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:00:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢你！
