Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.92,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@华康少女文字W5\bord0\fs30\1c&HA0CFCE&\pos(898,390)\frz285.5}来吃冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是什么样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 队长的性格啊男性关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚刚都说了 她只是我妈的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我又不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没怎么跟她聊过天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去买点高丽菜 帮我顾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 找零
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 您的找零
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能把钱给不认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很正经？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我感觉跟正经有点差别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪知道 那时候我还在上幼儿园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能当面问她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当面？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是请她接受采访
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聊着聊着转个弯把问题抛出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像艺人开记者会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交往顺利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要问我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 谁去采访问问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前好像也发生过类似的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不愿意 出发前晚在甲板上聊过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以为我们没看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你们关系挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那只是偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道你们关系不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不是不好吧 怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有距离啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你们在甲板上聊过天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你们关系挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那只是偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们本来就都不擅长说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以贵子一离开 我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没有孩子 不知道该跟她聊什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再说了 贵子实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的不想跟她聊聊贵子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子总是说 妈妈在等她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搜索中止了 是我做的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让你们久等了 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉提了个不情之请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 报濑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她还有点别的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}摄影机就位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 你们打算问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天想采访一下队长的私生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜欢的食物 日常生活等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有恋爱之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是你喜欢什么样的男性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会回答和南极观测无关的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小吟 人家高中生在问你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请说说看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近播放数下滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的很重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耳朵好红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}队长 您刚洗完澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜欢什么入浴剂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老实说 喜欢什么类型？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}眼睛再大一点会不会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保持原样就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}据说已经进入南极圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太阳不会沉下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像云一样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 但她就是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算说是云
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高云 中云 低云也各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无聊透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好大的云呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}云可真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明抓不到 但抬个头就能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪懂那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还是能意会一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}确实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么回事 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}采访结果如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟她没关系 是我想问的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道队长和小渊泽的女儿关系还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是出于好奇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是还没有原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可是个大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是队长 有义务跟队员沟通确认的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:24.84,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天〇八〇〇至一二〇〇允许舰上运动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.40,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉超痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬天运动经常会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你懂了吗 像云一样是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多少少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快告诉我啊 到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难以 言传
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子 你是故意让我和那孩子独处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对啊 因为那孩子需要小吟的灵魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想听听你是怎么看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想听我说恨你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从妈妈登上民间观测船开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就问了她很多遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟她说南极观测还有很多危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你还是要去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道南极是个什么样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我那时是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你犯了什么错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是判断失误 才把我妈妈留在南极的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时别无选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 最后让我问一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是真心的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真心这么想的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才讨厌谈这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我根本不知道自己是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是…只是妈妈没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我每天的生活并没有变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和等她回来的每一天完全一样 什么都没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我日日夜夜都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彷佛自己还在等妈妈回来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要改变这种生活 我就得出发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去那片 比宇宙还要遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两舷慢速后退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两舷慢速后退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}撞上固定冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要冲过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是要开到冰上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 要先大幅度后退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两舷停止 两舷慢速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两舷停止 两舷慢速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冲进冰层里去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用船体的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}破坏冰层
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才叫破冰船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果冰层没碎怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就一直重复
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重复到冰层破碎为止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到南极真的好艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤其这一带是出了名的难靠岸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么偏偏要挑这个地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为只有这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极观测正规化 是在第二次世界大战后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道这些吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}战败国的日本想派遣观测队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多国家都对此不信任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再加上日本没什么发言权
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后被分到的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是被公认为不可能靠岸的东翁古尔岛这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是被刁难了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道有没有被刁难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过可能拐弯抹角地包含了这层意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就好像在说「日本人 你们有本事就来啊」似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听起来真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过大家听了都热血起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全日本募款资助计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}造船工人们呕心沥血造出了观测船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次一次又一次 绝不言弃奋力拚搏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像破开冰层一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步又一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二强速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还没 还早着呢 得一直到我们抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一年又一年 无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子 贵子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 小渊泽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.01,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是…美极了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:06.07,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そっと记した梦　言い訳ばかりして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:16.80,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ほったらかしにしていた　叶うのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:25.57,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何があるのかも　何が変わるのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:30.86,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}行ってみなきゃ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:38.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあ　一歩前に　踏み出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:45.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな梦を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:49.86,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:54.44,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真っ白な世界に　残したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:59.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最初の足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:09.05,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界の最果てで　転がっていく太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:14.96,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}南风はやがて岛を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:19.30,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}髪を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:30.66,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}小さな梦を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:35.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}愿えた　ツヨクツヨク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}履き惯れたスニーカー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:44.65,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}纽をギュッと缔め直して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:50.10,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}でかい梦を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:54.57,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:59.26,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}波に揺られてかたふりして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:04.19,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}进んでいくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:08.68,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}宇宙より远くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:06.07,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}偷偷记下了梦想 却只找了一堆借口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:16.80,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想到自己总是忘记梦想 就怕去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:25.57,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怕出什么事 怕有什么变故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:30.86,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但驻足不前 就什么都明白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:38.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向前一步 迈出勇敢的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:45.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想实现心底大大的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:49.86,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遥远不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:54.44,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想在那一片纯白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:59.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}留下我最初的脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:09.05,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}红红的一轮夕阳 沉入了世界的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:14.96,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}海面南风跨越万千岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:19.30,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}吹动起我的发梢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:30.66,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想实现心底小小的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:35.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用力再用力 向神明许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}穿上熟悉的运动鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:44.65,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}紧紧地系好鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:50.10,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想实现心底大大的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:54.57,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遥远不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:59.26,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就在波涛之中举杯高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:04.19,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}继续一步步前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:08.68,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去比宇宙更遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是真的真的真的 想为队长做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是她完全没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}队员哪帮得了队长 人家也不会让你帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把你的心情 交给一个你碰得到人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不对 没有这回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我之前是怎么塞进箱子里的 好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收拾好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你能睁眼说瞎话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要出去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小结 带上摄影机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能下去感受一下 半径5公尺以内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终点！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是你妈妈来过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羡慕吧 嫉妒吧 恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你们趾高气昂地嘲笑我 我也相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你们以不可能为由背叛我 我也没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样 我到南极了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羡慕吧！嫉妒吧！恨吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活该！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就想说这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}压抑了很久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么关系 这才是报濑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活该
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活该
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2 活该
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2 活该
Comment: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:24.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}长いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:35.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:41.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}间违っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:52.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　仆は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:23:03.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}污れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:14.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言叶も　きっと见つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:19.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって构わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:25.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:24.85,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}寻找着漫长隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:35.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向着泛着微光气味的方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:41.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走错了 也别忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:52.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}从这里开始 我将踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:23:03.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}紧紧捏住手心里 脏脏的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:14.36,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}没说出口的话 我也一定会找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:19.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}随你们嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:25.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 迈出脚步
